WEBVTT

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:47.270
Well, good evening, family. Thank you

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.590
for joining me again tonight.

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:52.030
I wasn't going to do a video tonight;

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:53.830
I was going to

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:56.110
take the day off, but I felt in my

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.790
spirit we could just talk over some

00:01:57.800 --> 00:01:59.510
things real quick

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:01.430
and we'll pray.

00:02:01.440 --> 00:02:06.110
We saw a lot of progress in our prayers

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:08.469
for the nations even from the last 48

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:09.669
hours

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:12.110
when we did those back-to-back videos.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:14.390
I told you I believe with all my heart

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:16.670
God has assembled the greatest prayer

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:19.510
group of any generation for

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.390
such a time as this

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:24.310
with people like you.

00:02:24.320 --> 00:02:25.949
He said, "Braden, I'm bringing my

00:02:25.959 --> 00:02:27.590
best,"and

00:02:27.600 --> 00:02:29.630
I truly believe it,

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:32.990
that the veterans and the

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.510
newbies, the ones that are learning how

00:02:34.520 --> 00:02:36.910
to pray, I'm telling you, I really

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.350
believe we're changing things.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:40.750
And so,

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:42.470
finding these weapons of mass

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:44.990
destruction has been on my heart all

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:48.270
day. I truly believe they're in the

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:50.030
northeast,

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:52.110
underneath this mountain.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:55.110
I keep seeing this mountain.

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.070
And if you go back

00:02:57.080 --> 00:02:59.030
to what we were looking at yesterday,

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:01.710
I'll give a little recap real quick.

00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:04.949
I saw the man with the black hat

00:03:04.959 --> 00:03:06.550
hiding.

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:09.830
I don't know; it sounds like they

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:11.390
found him today.

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:13.990
I don't know if this is true. I'm

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.990
getting a lot of fake news, so

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.830
you don't know who is real

00:03:18.830 --> 00:03:18.840
and who

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:20.790
is

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:22.949
not, but some

00:03:22.959 --> 00:03:25.390
people say that he was injured and they

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:28.270
took his leg. Benny Johnson on his

00:03:28.270 --> 00:03:28.280
show

00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.830
tonight was saying that they believe

00:03:30.840 --> 00:03:32.470
that he was injured and they might have

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:34.070
taken his leg off because of the

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:36.670
injuries that he's sustained. I don't

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.750
know if that's fake news or not,

00:03:38.760 --> 00:03:40.390
but

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:44.350
as I continue to pray, I believe

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:45.870
that the Lord is going to deal with this

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:47.430
man, too.

00:03:47.440 --> 00:03:49.509
Some people say he's worse than the last

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:50.509
one.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:54.910
There's so much news. There's so much

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:57.830
stuff coming in

00:03:57.830 --> 00:03:57.840
that I said,

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:58.990
"What do you believe and what do you not

00:03:58.990 --> 00:03:59.000
believe?"You

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:00.310
have to really just

00:04:00.320 --> 00:04:02.430
filter it and go with what

00:04:02.440 --> 00:04:03.910
you're praying over.

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:06.670
President Trump declaring that he

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:09.190
believes the war is over; the economy, like

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:12.270
I told you—Israel hit, from what I

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:14.230
understand,

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:16.430
every oil

00:04:16.430 --> 00:04:16.440
and

00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:20.509
gas plant in Iran.

00:04:20.519 --> 00:04:21.990
And

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:23.750
if that is true, if they've hit every

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:25.990
single one of them, this is exactly what

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:29.190
the Lord showed us in our

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:32.990
prayer time back in June of last year.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:35.790
And he told us that Israel would strike

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.670
all the oil wells

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:40.030
and the oil refineries,

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.630
and there would be war on

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:47.230
the Strait of Hormuz.

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:54.743
We see

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:58.470
that happening.

00:04:58.480 --> 00:05:01.030
Oil went up to

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:05.790
$120 a barrel today

00:05:05.800 --> 00:05:07.710
as

00:05:07.720 --> 00:05:10.030
crude was skyrocketing

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:12.870
because of the news of Israel, and then

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:16.630
Iran hit one of Israel's main oil plants

00:05:16.640 --> 00:05:18.230
and their gas plants where they make

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:20.630
diesel and everything else. They hit

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:22.590
their largest plant, from what I

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:24.430
understood last night.

00:05:24.440 --> 00:05:26.750
So, they struck their oil

00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:29.390
wells; they blew up

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:30.950
all of theirs.

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:33.590
When that happened, oil shot up to

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:36.990
$120 a barrel. Now, President Trump

00:05:36.990 --> 00:05:37.000
came

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.670
on and said, "The war is over. It looks

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:41.670
like we're about over."Then oil

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:42.990
started going back down when

00:05:42.990 --> 00:05:43.000
he and

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.790
Putin said they

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:48.030
were coming to an agreement on

00:05:48.040 --> 00:05:51.390
lifting the sanctions off of the oil for

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:52.870
trade with

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:54.349
Russia,

00:05:54.840 --> 00:05:57.310
which

00:05:57.320 --> 00:06:00.630
I know

00:06:00.640 --> 00:06:02.790
President Trump probably is trying to

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:04.470
help our economy and he doesn't want

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.030
people mad at him because

00:06:06.040 --> 00:06:09.390
midterms are coming. If you have gas

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:13.510
lines and

00:06:13.510 --> 00:06:13.520
$10-a-gallon

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:16.790
gas, you're going to have a

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:19.470
lot of upset Americans.

00:06:23.200 --> 00:06:25.350
As we're praying into these things and

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:27.310
seeing it, I believe

00:06:27.320 --> 00:06:30.990
the visions that the Lord shows me are

00:06:30.990 --> 00:06:31.000
so

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.190
prayer changes

00:06:34.190 --> 00:06:34.200
things—that

00:06:34.200 --> 00:06:36.510
we don't have the gas lines, that

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:38.990
we don't have massive

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:41.710
gas prices go above $10 a gallon, and the

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:43.510
anti-Semitism and all the things that

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:47.070
the Lord has shown me. I know because

00:06:47.080 --> 00:06:48.390
part of the vision has already come

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:49.830
true.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:55.110
The war with Iran, the striking of

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:56.909
all the oil wells—that part of the

00:06:56.919 --> 00:06:58.670
vision has happened, manifested

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:00.550
completely.

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:04.030
The gas lines and oil going to $200 a

00:07:04.030 --> 00:07:04.040
barrel—this

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:05.870
is the part where it

00:07:05.880 --> 00:07:07.630
split.

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:09.710
And so far it only

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:12.030
went to $120.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.030
No gas lines.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:16.390
It's interesting to me,

00:07:16.400 --> 00:07:18.310
the things that I see and we're praying

00:07:18.320 --> 00:07:20.430
over.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:23.110
Between all channels,

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.909
we had probably 150,000 people pray over

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:27.470
that last night.

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:33.470
I'm not

00:07:33.480 --> 00:07:36.350
quite to 200,000, but

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:38.830
just a little under with all seven

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:40.030
channels.

00:07:40.030 --> 00:07:40.040
I

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:42.150
give all the glory to

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:43.350
God. There's

00:07:43.360 --> 00:07:44.790
so many of you that come out and pray

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:47.110
like that. I

00:07:47.120 --> 00:07:49.030
know the power of prayer. If you get

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:51.270
one of us to pray, good; two agreeing

00:07:51.270 --> 00:07:51.280
touching

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:53.150
anything... just think about

00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:55.790
almost 200,000 people praying

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:58.190
for up to

00:07:58.190 --> 00:07:58.200
two

00:07:58.200 --> 00:07:59.710
or

00:07:59.710 --> 00:07:59.720
three

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:02.870
hours.

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:04.430
That's amazing.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:06.590
I

00:08:06.600 --> 00:08:08.150
believe that we're changing

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:11.710
things.

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:17.990
I pray we don't see gas go up to $10 a

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:20.230
gallon. That would be terrible

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:21.870
and it would

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:23.790
affect our economy

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:27.590
greatly. Half of it is in the news,

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:29.070
half of it's not. The power of

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.670
prayer there. Number two,

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:35.070
the Lord showed us yesterday,

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:39.390
I believe, one weapon.

00:08:39.400 --> 00:08:42.390
And as I was in the spirit again,

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:44.470
I could hear

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:47.270
that new leader talking to a

00:08:47.280 --> 00:08:48.750
scientist.

00:08:48.760 --> 00:08:51.390
"Does it

00:08:51.390 --> 00:08:51.400
work?"I

00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:53.950
could hear him in English. "Does it

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:55.430
work?"The

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:57.750
scientist, in a

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:00.270
white outfit,

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:11.470
said, "It has not been tested

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.910
yet,

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:17.790
but we believe we have successfully

00:09:17.800 --> 00:09:19.950
built the

00:09:24.310 --> 00:09:24.320
bomb."It

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:32.510
was ready to put on a rocket; it

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:36.190
looked as long as a school bus, like

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:38.070
a massive

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:40.390
city bus.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:42.350
That's how big this thing

00:09:42.350 --> 00:09:42.360
was—a

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:45.390
fat,

00:09:45.400 --> 00:09:47.710
round-looking rocket.

00:09:47.720 --> 00:09:49.230
They were pointing at this rocket

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:51.430
saying that could be the payload.

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:53.830
They were discussing

00:09:53.840 --> 00:09:56.030
this one thing.

00:09:56.040 --> 00:09:58.230
They only had one,

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:01.390
but it was not tested.

00:10:01.400 --> 00:10:03.230
They said, "So,

00:10:03.240 --> 00:10:05.190
we don't know

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:07.150
if it will work,

00:10:07.160 --> 00:10:12.950
but we all believe that it will.

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:16.870
We only have

00:10:16.870 --> 00:10:16.880
one."And

00:10:16.880 --> 00:10:19.430
I believe that was a nuclear

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:20.750
something.

00:10:20.760 --> 00:10:25.350
If you go back to what the Lord said:

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:28.470
Hiroshima.

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:31.870
Go back to that. That was an atom

00:10:31.870 --> 00:10:31.880
bomb.

00:10:31.880 --> 00:10:33.590
It wasn't like what we have now, these

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.350
great big ones,

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:37.110
but it was still something very

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.277
significant

00:10:39.287 --> 00:10:39.470
that

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:41.470
hit

00:10:41.480 --> 00:10:44.110
Japan in World War II.

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.990
The Lord

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.550
told us this,

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:51.990
but as I was hearing this

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:54.750
scientist talking to

00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:56.510
the man with the black hat, black

00:10:56.520 --> 00:10:58.470
turban, they kept talking back and

00:10:58.480 --> 00:10:59.510
forth:

00:10:59.520 --> 00:11:01.990
"What do we have at our disposal? What

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.070
bigger artillery do we have

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:05.870
underground?"They

00:11:05.880 --> 00:11:08.470
were discussing things,

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:10.910
getting ready

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:13.230
for a surprise

00:11:13.240 --> 00:11:17.350
attack against Israel

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:21.670
with biological weapons.

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:24.390
I saw biological weapons. I saw

00:11:24.400 --> 00:11:26.110
containers

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.470
that were underneath the ground.

00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:32.310
They were separated out by Agent Orange.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:34.310
And there were three different kind of

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.190
things.

00:11:42.360 --> 00:11:44.270
The first one looked like

00:11:44.270 --> 00:11:44.280
a

00:11:44.280 --> 00:11:46.070
mustard-yellow

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:48.350
substance

00:11:48.360 --> 00:11:50.070
because the Lord highlighted it with a

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:51.590
color.

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:55.190
It was in a black drum,

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:57.830
but in the spirit I could see a color on

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:59.590
it.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:03.270
The next one was red.

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:05.270
They only had about six or seven

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:09.750
barrels stacked up three high.

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:20.270
The others were over here and I could

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:21.750
see them

00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:24.270
being stored, but there was a lot

00:12:24.280 --> 00:12:26.350
of it—50

00:12:26.350 --> 00:12:26.360
or

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:30.110
60 barrels or more.

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:36.590
This one looked red,

00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:40.590
and I saw on it the letter Y.

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:42.510
I'm

00:12:42.520 --> 00:12:44.510
still praying about it, but it was

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:45.910
some kind of

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:48.350
biological

00:12:48.360 --> 00:12:49.829
weapon,

00:12:49.839 --> 00:12:51.670
chemical warfare.

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:56.710
It was right next to it. That

00:12:56.720 --> 00:12:58.390
was something in the spirit realm. When I

00:12:58.400 --> 00:12:59.990
was looking at it, there was something that looked like

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:03.070
another kind of

00:13:03.070 --> 00:13:03.080
object,

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:05.710
but I couldn't focus on it.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:08.070
The visions come very fast

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:09.710
and whenever I'm looking, so many

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:11.510
things are coming at me. I don't take

00:13:11.520 --> 00:13:14.030
the time, because I'm on a live stream, to pause

00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:17.350
it and try to look into it.

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:19.030
That's the trouble with being

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:20.710
live.

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:23.990
If it were in my private time, I would

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.070
spend all day on that

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:28.150
because I pray over it, and

00:13:30.320 --> 00:13:32.990
what I've learned to do is

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.750
freeze-frame it in the

00:13:34.760 --> 00:13:37.830
spirit and just pray specifically over

00:13:37.840 --> 00:13:42.590
those biological weapons for hours

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.110
and be able to focus in and look around

00:13:45.120 --> 00:13:46.630
them. It

00:13:46.630 --> 00:13:46.640
is

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:49.150
all by the Spirit of God,

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:51.870
all to the glory of God.

00:13:51.880 --> 00:13:54.190
I didn't do that last night, though I wish

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:56.150
I would have now.

00:13:57.400 --> 00:13:59.350
I saw the missiles.

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:01.550
They were painted black.

00:14:01.560 --> 00:14:05.750
Some were big,

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:08.630
some were small.

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:12.110
I believe with all my heart this is

00:14:12.120 --> 00:14:14.230
under a mountain

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:17.710
in the northeast

00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:20.750
area of

00:14:20.750 --> 00:14:20.760
Iran,

00:14:20.760 --> 00:14:23.270
closer to Afghanistan.

00:14:25.750 --> 00:14:25.760
Turkmenistan

00:14:31.040 --> 00:14:32.510
is

00:14:35.920 --> 00:14:37.910
northeast up here, and this is

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:40.790
Afghanistan. If I can see

00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:42.150
the map?

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:44.030
I'm talking about

00:14:44.030 --> 00:14:44.040
the

00:14:44.040 --> 00:14:46.870
north-northeast

00:14:46.870 --> 00:14:46.880
area.

00:14:46.880 --> 00:14:48.510
So

00:14:54.680 --> 00:14:59.870
it had to be

00:14:59.870 --> 00:14:59.880
Turkmenistan.

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:02.590
I see Iran and the mountains.

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:04.710
In this vision,

00:15:04.720 --> 00:15:07.470
I saw mountains

00:15:07.480 --> 00:15:12.030
and I kept seeing northeast.

00:15:12.040 --> 00:15:15.390
It was underneath these

00:15:15.390 --> 00:15:15.400
mountains—great

00:15:15.400 --> 00:15:18.270
facilities.

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:21.430
It doesn't matter anymore; I'm

